Bear decal letters of the taxicab company, association, or fleet name and fleet vehicle number, if applicable, or the name of the owner and independent taxicab number, if applicable, which shall be on the rear of the body so as to be clearly visible
        from the rear, on either side of and in alignment with the center of the vehicle manufacturer placed logo. The decal letters shall be the color black, in Calibri font, using capital letters that are one and one half (1-1/2) inches in height measured
        from the X height and manufactured of 3M Controltac Plus Film (or equivalent);
